data.message: I am caught up from last week’s orders! Thank you all for your patience. ❤️ lesson learned, don’t try to run a business while hooked to IV pain medication! 😂 Anywho, back to a 24 hour turn around time. Shipping is going out later today! If you ordered and haven’t heard from me, send me another PM. ❤️

Final day of the super extended $15 sale! $15 alone $20 with 5 gel packs - shipping additional $7-$10 depending on if you add gel or not! ***if you haven’t received an invoice, please PM me. Last week was obviously crazy, and I think I am caught up 🤞🏼

Winner Of the Mother’s Day contest!! She tagged her friend Vanessa, Lluvia was the random # 75 so they both win! ❤️🌹❤️ (Next time I will be more prepared, I promise!) My phone went from 100% to 58% playing the Kevin Bacon game. That was fun!😂
Winner winner chicken dinner!

Almost ready for the 10,000 time on the winning post! 😂 I’d love to say I’m never doing this again, but you all know me, and I’ll probably try it again 😂  The list is long, hand written and I’ll be picking a number live and finally announcing a winner in a bit! We had to go through one by one and make sure every person who went on the list followed the rules! 🙌🏼❤️
Have you ordered your Car Seat Cooler yet? 😱
Halppppppppp

Of course FB is only showing me 149 comments 😂😭 It will be a bit to find the winner... this is what I was trying to explain, I have to click “all comments”, and some are flagged as spam, again, thanks FB! Potential winning number is 554, I just need to check it. I want to make sure I have full transparency here! ❤️
Mother’s Day winner!
As usual, I’m running behind. Give me until 7pm. Sorry, been a strange day. I’m going live to pick the winner, so that should be fun 😂
Picking the Mother’s Day winner tomorrow at 5! Be sure to get all of your tags in! 🙌🏼

I’m home, finally! I’m going to start reaching out to everyone to come pick up orders. If you have my address, and we’ve already talked go ahead and come over. Let me know when you get here and I’ll run your order out to you! ❤️🙌🏼

I’m still in the hospital. Trying to coordinate with @billmeola on when we can schedule picking up orders. He’s busy playing mom and dad right now, so bare with us. Thank you all for your patience and understanding in this confusing time. ❤️ I’m sure I can figure something out if you need your order before I break loose out of here. (Could Be Saturday at the earliest😫) send me a PM or text.
Sorry for ghosting everyone today. I’ve been at Del We for hours, and am now being admitted. 😫 My reminder that Lupus is real, and she’ll slow you down! I’m hoping to be home tomorrow ❤️

Mothers Day Post!! Tag another momma that you know. Follow the rules at the bottom!! Whoever wins, that tag, you both win! We’ve got warmers, 2 big Gold Canyon Candles, a custom tumbler, Dutch Bros. gift card, bath / body set (courtesy of one of our customers/ friends!), flowers, Nothing Bunt Cakes gift card, and so much more!! I’ll be updating as more arrives! Already over $150 in prizes!! Insane!! You can tag as many times as you want! ****secondary prize for shares! $25 credit to waldos!  

You both must “like” @waldoswarmers,  https://www.facebook.com/Ts.KoatedCreations/  https://www.facebook.com/groups/413622739033929/?ref=share
Crossing fingers 🤞🏼 Messages are back up! 🙌🏼

FB has been crappy for the last 24 hours. It’s hit or miss. My business page messages aren’t loading! Yesterday some of my replies weren’t sending. 😐 This is all I see. I’ve tried to reply through my personal page, so check your “other” or “filtered” folders. I see the notifications come through on my phone, but they don’t load. It’s been like this off and on for over a week. Jennifer Meola - check for that name! 🙌🏼❤️

Do me a solid and read this in the familiar deep / intriguing “movie announcer” voice —— “A family divided, Marvel VS Star Wars... who will win?”  Haha!! I’ve been inundated with messages. Flash sale! $15 or $20 with 5 gel packs. $6 alone or $10 if shipping with gel packs additional for shipping... folder is up and current. Send me a pic of the one (multiples ok!) you would like to order with your email for invoice. I get them made as fast as I can! They will be made in the order of payment received. Remember you CAN use these on your seat too! I have kids and adult prints! *I make the gel packs optional since a lot of people have them already* this will be the last sale until mid June!
